Class Description
AirportRhapsody
Main class for the Airport Rhapsody Problem.
ALPassenger
Arrival Lounge Passenger Interface
ALPorter
Arrival Lounge Porter Interface
ArrivalLounge
Implementation of the Arrival Lounge Shared Memory The passengers arrive here and get the whole airport moving.
ArrivalQuay
Implementation of the Arrival Quay Shared Memory The BusDriver waits here for passengers to come so he can drive them to departure terminal.
ArrivalTerminalExit
Implementation of the Arrival Terminal Exit Shared Memory The Passengers arrive here and wait other passengers to reach final state so they can progress.
ATEPassenger
Arrival Terminal Exit Passenger Interface
ATTQBusDriver
Arrival Terminal Transfer Quay BusDriver Interface
ATTQPassenger
Arrival Terminal Transfer Quay Passenger Interface
BagColPoint
Implementation of the Baggage Collection Point Shared Memory The passenger come here to fetch their baggage, put on the conveyor belt by the porter.
BagRecOffice
Implementation of the Baggage Reclaim Office Shared Memory The passenger comes here in case he loses any baggage, to report the occurrence.
BCPPassenger
Baggage Collection Point Passenger Interface
BCPPorter
Baggage Collection Point Porter Interface
BROPassenger
Baggage Reclaim Office Passenger Interface
BusDriver
Bus Driver thread and life cycle.
BusDriverStates
Enum implementing the typical bus driver states: PARKING_AT_THE_ARRIVAL_TERMINAL - When the BusDriver is parked on the ArrivalQuay waiting for passengers DRIVING_FORWARD - Purely a transitional state, it represent when the bus driver is driving to the Departure Terminal PARKING_AT_THE_DEPARTURE_TERMINAL - When the BusDriver is parked on the DepartureQuay waiting for passengers to drop off DRIVING_BACKWARD - Represents the drive back to the ArrivalQuay
DepartureQuay

Implementation of the Departure Terminal Entrance Shared Memory The Passengers arrive here and wait other passengers to reach final state so they can progress.
